reviewText: The Instructor's platform and the Clickup webpage did not align, and it was confusing for a beginner.

This course needs major updating. The course doesn't match the current ClickUp platform as of 12/2022 which makes it extremely difficult to follow along with. Additionally, while trying to navigate ClickUp, it continually crashed. Perhaps this course was relevant previously but I definitely would not recommend it at this point in time. Nor would I recommend ClickUp. I can't imagine using an app that crashes this much as a project tracker for a business.
